---
title: The Alchemist's Hearth
layout: layouts/base
section: "alchemists-hearth"
---

<section class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 space-y-12">

  <header class="space-y-4">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-ink">The Alchemist's Hearth</h1>
    <p class="text-lead text-ink-secondary max-w-xl">
      My kitchen experiments, cooking failures, and the occasional dish that
      actually turns out great.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose-site text-ink-secondary">
    <p>
      I love cooking. Sometimes things work out, sometimes they don't. This is
      where I write about what I'm making, recipes I'm trying, and whatever
      I'm learning as I go.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're into cooking or just curious, welcome. Let's see what we
      can burn together.
    </p>
  </div>

  <ol class="index-list list-none m-0 p-0">
    {% for post in collections.alchemistsHearth %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="index-row">
          <h2 class="index-row__title">{{ post.data.title | smartTitleCase }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="index-row__desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>

</section>
